      "content": "hey so i was just cleaning my ears with a qtip and i heard this weird loud pop in my left ear. now my left ear feels totally blocked like i cant hear anything at all through it but it doesnt really hurt. i think it might just be some wax or maybe just ringing/tinnitus stuff? do u think it'll just go away on its own or something?",
